data.description: Beautiful! Newly updated throughout! 4 bedroom, 3 bath home offers over 2400SF of spacious living. Light and bright, large living room with triple window overlooks pretty, treed front yard and opens to formal dining room with views to backyard and deck. Beautiful all new kitchen includes new soft-shut white cupboards w/nickel hardware, new granite, SS Sink, SS Range/Oven and Dishwasher.  Primary bedroom with updated private full bath includes new vanity. 2 additional guest bedrooms on main level share newly updated hall bath.  Take a few steps downstairs and discover a large family room with brick fireplace with wood burning insert.  A new patio door leads out to the beautiful wooded large yard.  The lower level also has a large bedroom with full bath in hall and storage closet, plus laundry closet.  This level walks out to garage.  This floor plan would work for multi-generational living as both levels have generous living spaces. Many updates before market release include entire interior freshly painted and all new flooring throughout.  New light fixtures (most) throughout. New lower-level patio door.  New roof in 2023 and new commercial grade gutters with leaf guard.  Fabulous location, nestled in the heart of a serene, beautiful neighborhood, convenient to everything, close to Fenton and Downtown.  Don't wait, this won't last. Professional photos coming. Showings to start Thursday 25th.
